      ["Example: Adjusted Capital Allocation", "Net income allocated and withdrawals recorded; updated capital balances reflect partner equity accurately."],
      ["Example: Real-Life Scenario", "Two partners allocate quarterly profits based on capital contribution and performance ratio."],
      ["Example: Decision Based on Ratios", "Investors may decide to invest in a partnership with strong ROE and manageable debt-to-equity ratio."]
